                                I’m most effective in roles where web experience, data, and strategy intersect—such as
                                website optimization, CRO, SEO, and growth-focused web marketing. I enjoy working on
                                high-impact surfaces that directly influence acquisition, engagement, and revenue.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Are you more technical or more strategic?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                Both—and that’s intentional. I’m comfortable working directly with HTML, CSS,
                                JavaScript, analytics, and experimentation tools, but I focus on why we’re building
                                something just as much as how. The goal is business impact, not technical novelty.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Why not use a CMS or website builder for this site?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                This site is intentionally custom-built to demonstrate how I think about performance,
                                scalability, and maintainability. For many organizations, a CMS is the right choice—but
                                understanding what’s happening under the hood is critical to making good decisions at
                                scale.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            What makes you different from other web marketers?
                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq__answer">
                            <p>
                                I focus on outcomes, not outputs. I care about conversion rates, discoverability, and
                                system-level improvements—not just launches. I also prioritize clean execution and
                                long-term maintainability over quick wins that don’t scale.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="faq__item">
                        <summary class="faq__question">
                            Is this site still a work in progress?
                        </summary>
